.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, tea, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, hiking, drawing, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person drinking water##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee        | water    | iced-tea | tea      |
| Hobby   | card-games        | sudoku   | hiking  | drawing  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball | soccer   | climbing |

