.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, artichoke, cranberry, orange
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, thriller
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, gardening, baking
1. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating apple##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person eating artichoke is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | apple     | orange   | cranberry | artichoke |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | superhero | fantasy   |
| Hobby           | baking    | magic-tricks     | cooking      | gardening     |

